entry.title: multigraph/userguide
entry.summary:
Source code for the original, docbook-based, Multigraph user guide.

This is the source code for the old, docbook-based, copy of the Multigraph user guide --- the one that appears on www.multigraph.org. This code isn't used any more, but I've uploaded it here for reference while writing a new manual.
